  "2026-06-04T07:19:28.785Z",codex-sdk-continuation,"Evidence: refreshed live Sentry gate expected handled CLI classifier. Verification passed: tests/integration/release-automation-contract.spec.ts, live node scripts/release/sentry-telemetry-gate.mjs --json with critical=0 high=0, telemetry stack health with 15110 events in last 24h, and pnpm build."
